review: First, I can’t pull up the pictures because everytime I do it says “Can’t open file” and then I’m super bothered that I’m getting messages that someone is looking at my pictures. When I look up the privacy info it looks like everybody and their mother ther can look at my pictures. I have my grandkids pictures and I do want some pedofiler looking at my grandchildren. What kind of app is this. I’m going to find another app to transfer my pictures out of this one. SHAME ON YOU
title: This app has so many issues

review: I paid the removal of ads a year ago. The app is simply designed and that’s what I looked for. However, I’m getting ads and now they have a monthly subscription for the removal of ads when I already paid a license for the app. Not only they disrespect buyers, but now crave for monthly payments. I might as well just use the native gallery.
title: Ads after paying
developerResponse: {'id': 39763037, 'body': 'Hi! Thank you for your review and for letting us know.\nPlease, reach out to our Customer Support Team at support.galleryvaultios@zipoapps.com and we will do our best to look into the issue for you.\nThank you!', 'modified': '2023-10-26T21:11:14Z'}

review: I have put password on it and done everything it has asked and the only notifications I get is someone is looking for your photos allow us to secure them. Wth does that even mean??? It is already supposed to be secure!!!!!

developerResponse:
{'id': 42402186, 'body': 'Hi,
Thank you for your review.
